    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i need some perspective on something weird at work. so i've been pushing back on some of the compliance stuff lately, and like, right after i did that, they gave me this huge promotion and a corner office. does that seem suspicious to you? like, why would they reward me for being difficult?",
