      "content": "it's exactly that. it feels so scripted. like, even the way they phrased the announcement in the team meeting was weirdly vague, almost like they were trying to hide the real reason. i'm starting to feel like i'm not even an employee anymore, just a project they're managing. if this is actually a way to keep me under their thumb, what should i even be looking for? how would someone even prove a company is doing this on purpose?",
